SIMPLE: postmaster
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Postmaster
<hw>Post"mas`ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who has charge of a station for the accommodation of travelers; one who
supplies post horses.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who has charge of a post office, and the
distribution and forwarding of mails.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Postmaster-general</ent>⟦br⟧
